@startuml Sequence_Statistics

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Analytics API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Redis Cache" as Cache

== Admin View Statistics ==
User -> Client: Access admin dashboard
Client -> API: GET /api/admin/statistics
API -> Cache: Check cache

alt Data in cache
    Cache --> API: Cached statistics
    API --> Client: Return cached data
else Data not in cache
    Cache --> API: Cache miss
    API -> DB: Query user statistics
    DB --> API: User stats
    API -> DB: Query product statistics
    DB --> API: Product stats
    API -> DB: Query revenue data
    DB --> API: Revenue stats
    API -> API: Aggregate statistics
    API -> Cache: Store in cache
    API --> Client: Return statistics
end

Client --> User: Display charts and stats

== Seller View Statistics ==
User -> Client: Access seller dashboard
Client -> API: GET /api/sellers/statistics
API -> DB: Get seller products stats
DB --> API: Product statistics
API -> DB: Get seller customers
DB --> API: Customer data
API -> DB: Get seller revenue
DB --> API: Revenue data
API --> Client: Return statistics
Client --> User: Display seller stats

@enduml

